💧💎 Active Auction two posts back. 💎💧 Double Bubbler with 2-to-4 hole percolators. Having half the air flow in the first chamber acts as a regulator for the 4-hole in the second one. This allows for soft, fluttery bubbles that regain flavor and provide just enough cooling of the vapor to enable a longer draw from the piece. This piece is meant to function optimally when a capped-off banger is on it, making it designed with the user in mind from the inside out!

Thank you so much @mainglassman for allowing me to finally end my search for this image. Here’s another piece I made in my class at Penland with @carmenlozar. Carmen presented us with this cobalt blue glass base as a jumping board for any idea we could think of. I immediately envision a little figure diving. I’m so fortunate I went with my instinct- I say this very rarely, but it came out exactly how I pictured and I couldn’t be any happier with the outcome. I really love how simple, yet expressive it is. And with this one idea came a million more! Thanks for looking ✨
